1
00:00:28,360 --> 00:00:29,360
Over a decade ago,

2
00:00:29,400 --> 00:00:30,960
a great chaos erupted in the Immortal Realm.

3
00:00:30,960 --> 00:00:33,330
I risked my life to escort Yao'er to escape to the Lower Realm.

4
00:00:33,330 --> 00:00:34,330
My origin was heavily damaged,

5
00:00:34,330 --> 00:00:35,800
and my cultivation is less than a tenth of what it was.

6
00:00:35,800 --> 00:00:37,660
I still haven't fully recovered.

7
00:00:37,730 --> 00:00:40,960
I thought the Su family in this remote corner could be a safe haven.

8
00:00:40,960 --> 00:00:42,960
Who knew Yao'er was still immature

9
00:00:43,330 --> 00:00:45,400
and provoked a vicious fiend like Gu Linyuan.

10
00:00:45,400 --> 00:00:46,600
Get up, Su Changkong.

11
00:00:46,630 --> 00:00:47,630
I don't blame you.

12
00:00:48,430 --> 00:00:50,160
This devastating disaster for the Su family

13
00:00:50,160 --> 00:00:52,000
is all because of Yao'er's caprice.

14
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:53,730
It is truly an undeserved catastrophe.

15
00:00:53,730 --> 00:00:55,230
As her mother,

16
00:00:55,430 --> 00:00:56,060
this karma

17
00:00:56,130 --> 00:00:57,900
should indeed be settled by me.

18
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:58,760
Wanqing.

19
00:00:59,060 --> 00:01:00,900
It is I, Su Changkong, who am incompetent.

20
00:01:00,900 --> 00:01:02,000
I have let you down.

21
00:01:07,460 --> 00:01:08,330
Did you hear?

22
00:01:08,630 --> 00:01:09,860
The Eldest Miss's double pupils

23
00:01:09,860 --> 00:01:12,760
were forcibly gouged out by the Gu family's patriarch.

24
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:14,600
She's now a blind invalid.

25
00:01:14,700 --> 00:01:15,400
Shh.

26
00:01:15,560 --> 00:01:16,730
Keep your voice down.

27
00:01:16,730 --> 00:01:17,530
In three days,

28
00:01:17,700 --> 00:01:19,800
the Gu patriarch will massacre the Su family.

29
00:01:19,800 --> 00:01:21,530
Let's slip away early tonight.

30
00:01:24,930 --> 00:01:25,930
Great.

31
00:01:26,360 --> 00:01:27,530
Yao'er is blind.

32
00:01:28,300 --> 00:01:31,230
This is the perfect time for me to be her only support.

33
00:01:31,330 --> 00:01:32,729
I finally have the chance

34
00:01:32,900 --> 00:01:34,860
to be by her side openly.

35
00:01:39,130 --> 00:01:39,900
Feng,

36
00:01:40,700 --> 00:01:41,800
do not miss me.

37
00:01:42,759 --> 00:01:44,400
Our mortal destiny is over.

38
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:47,330
See you on the path to immortality.

39
00:01:50,330 --> 00:01:52,190
I used to devote myself to the Dao,

40
00:01:53,300 --> 00:01:55,500
determined to reach the absolute peak.

41
00:01:56,259 --> 00:02:00,060
But I watched helplessly as my true love died at the hands of my enemy.

42
00:02:00,130 --> 00:02:00,760
Yao'er,

43
00:02:01,460 --> 00:02:02,960
you are her reincarnation.

44
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:03,730
In this life,

45
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:05,700
I am willing to hide my pride

46
00:02:05,930 --> 00:02:07,300
and be a humble groom

47
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:09,400
just to protect you on your path to immortality.

48
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:11,230
Gu Linyuan took your double pupils,

49
00:02:11,230 --> 00:02:12,960
then I will restore your sight.

50
00:02:14,300 --> 00:02:16,030
Pass down my War King's decree.

51
00:02:16,260 --> 00:02:18,829
Go and fetch my Innate Resurgence Divine Water.

52
00:02:18,829 --> 00:02:20,000
In three days,

53
00:02:20,730 --> 00:02:22,390
I will give Yao'er a surprise.

54
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:25,060
What are you doing?

55
00:02:25,500 --> 00:02:26,260
Who knows.

56
00:02:26,430 --> 00:02:28,400
He became stupid from feeding horses.

57
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:31,760
The host has successfully harvested the primal yin of the Great Emperor's own daughter.

58
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:32,820
Yin and Yang merge.

59
00:02:33,300 --> 00:02:35,560
Cultivation breaks through to the late Quasi-Emperor stage,

60
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:38,220
only one step away from the Great Emperor Realm.

61
00:02:40,660 --> 00:02:41,660
Thank you, Madam,

62
00:02:41,829 --> 00:02:43,030
for helping me with my cultivation.

63
00:02:43,030 --> 00:02:44,230
Don't think that because of this,

64
00:02:44,230 --> 00:02:45,060
I will forgive you

65
00:02:45,060 --> 00:02:46,760
for your transgressive and frivolous behavior last night.

66
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:47,760
In just one night,

67
00:02:47,900 --> 00:02:49,430
he broke through to the late Quasi-Emperor stage.

68
00:02:49,430 --> 00:02:50,030
Doesn't that mean

69
00:02:50,030 --> 00:02:50,930
he is now

70
00:02:51,260 --> 00:02:52,160
only one step away from the Emperor Realm?

71
00:02:52,160 --> 00:02:52,760
Moreover,

72
00:02:53,060 --> 00:02:54,600
it was you who helped my cultivation.

73
00:02:54,600 --> 00:02:55,900
By borrowing your origin,

74
00:02:55,900 --> 00:02:57,600
I am also close to touching the threshold of the Quasi-Emperor.

75
00:02:57,600 --> 00:02:59,630
How about you work a little harder, Madam.

76
00:02:59,630 --> 00:03:00,160
Tonight,

77
00:03:00,200 --> 00:03:01,760
I will break through to the Quasi-Emperor.

78
00:03:01,760 --> 00:03:02,930
Calculating the time,

79
00:03:02,930 --> 00:03:04,000
that guy Su Changkong

80
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,300
should be making a move soon.

81
00:03:05,300 --> 00:03:06,160
Reporting to the Master,

82
00:03:06,160 --> 00:03:07,360
Su Changkong, Master of the Su Family,

83
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:11,420
is kneeling outside the island with Fairy Lu, waiting for your audience.

84
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:16,400
Su Changkong,

85
00:03:16,460 --> 00:03:17,460
along with Lu Wanqing,

86
00:03:17,460 --> 00:03:18,990
pays respects to Master Gu.

87
00:03:19,600 --> 00:03:21,630
I beg you to show mercy

88
00:03:21,900 --> 00:03:23,700
and spare the Su Family.

89
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:28,300
Key plot character with top-tier fortune detected,

90
00:03:28,600 --> 00:03:29,500
Lu Wanqing.

91
00:03:30,630 --> 00:03:31,890
Hidden constitution:

92
00:03:31,900 --> 00:03:33,329
Innate Grand Lunar Body.

93
00:03:34,260 --> 00:03:36,500
If the host can subdue her and win her allegiance,

94
00:03:36,500 --> 00:03:39,100
a massive amount of heavenly fortune can be plundered.

95
00:03:39,100 --> 00:03:39,900
Su Changkong,

96
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:41,630
you came here early today.

97
00:03:41,630 --> 00:03:43,290
What do you have to beg me with?

98
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:45,060
I am willing to sever

99
00:03:45,060 --> 00:03:46,730
the Dao companion bond with Lu Wanqing,

100
00:03:46,730 --> 00:03:48,460
and leave her to your disposal.

101
00:03:48,829 --> 00:03:49,400
Today,

102
00:03:49,460 --> 00:03:51,060
the Xuantian Continent is devoid of spiritual energy.

103
00:03:51,060 --> 00:03:51,829
But Wanqing

104
00:03:51,930 --> 00:03:53,430
is a fairy from the Nine Heavens

105
00:03:53,430 --> 00:03:54,900
who fell to the mortal realm.

106
00:03:54,900 --> 00:03:56,160
Her Grand Lunar origin

107
00:03:56,230 --> 00:03:58,030
remains pure and flawless to this day,

108
00:03:58,030 --> 00:03:59,630
without the slightest loss.

109
00:03:59,930 --> 00:04:02,600
She can definitely help you break the shackles,

110
00:04:02,830 --> 00:04:04,130
break through to the Emperor Realm,

111
00:04:04,130 --> 00:04:05,990
and ascend to the Immortal Realm.

112
00:04:06,060 --> 00:04:07,960
Abandoning a Dao companion to her face.

113
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:08,960
This hypocrite

114
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:12,260
saves me a lot of effort in claiming his fortune.

115
00:04:12,500 --> 00:04:14,060
The secret of ascension to the Immortal Realm,

116
00:04:14,060 --> 00:04:15,630
I am indeed curious about it.

117
00:04:15,630 --> 00:04:16,459
But I haven't fallen to the point

118
00:04:16,459 --> 00:04:19,459
of needing to be told by a scum who abandons his wife for glory.

119
00:04:19,459 --> 00:04:20,260
Throw him out,

120
00:04:20,260 --> 00:04:21,790
and lock him in the dungeon.

121
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:29,030
Abandoned by your husband to your face,

122
00:04:29,030 --> 00:04:30,890
you don't seem surprised by this.

123
00:04:31,230 --> 00:04:32,860
I am willing to submit to you

124
00:04:33,060 --> 00:04:34,700
and hand over the Grand Lunar origin.

125
00:04:34,700 --> 00:04:36,800
The Su Family suffered an unprovoked disaster because of Yao'er.

126
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:38,360
I hope you keep your word

127
00:04:39,130 --> 00:04:40,400
and spare the Su Family.

128
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:42,600
I am a Quasi-Emperor of the current age,

129
00:04:42,630 --> 00:04:44,890
only half a step away from proving my Dao.

130
00:04:45,530 --> 00:04:46,730
Those who want to cling to me,

131
00:04:46,730 --> 00:04:49,400
the holy maidens and prodigies willing to offer their origins,

132
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:52,130
can line up from the Eastern Wasteland to the Western Desert.

133
00:04:52,130 --> 00:04:52,790
Do you think

134
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:54,659
I would fancy you?

135
00:04:55,200 --> 00:04:58,460
What if it's the secret of ascension to the Immortal Realm?

136
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:03,260
Madam,

137
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:05,900
you wouldn't want anything bad

138
00:05:05,900 --> 00:05:07,230
to happen to your daughter, would you?
